* Franz Schubert. ''Impromptus.'' Played on the 1810 Matthias Müller model piano and the 1830 Joseph Schantz piano. Label: Zig Zag Territorois. 
* 阿列克谢·卢比莫夫、尤里·马丁诺夫、奥尔加·马丁诺娃、亚历山德拉·科列涅娃、伊丽莎维塔·米勒、奥尔加·帕什琴科、阿列克谢·祖耶夫。 Ludwig van Beethoven. Complete piano sonatas. Played on copies of Stein ([[约翰·安德鲁斯·史坦因|约翰·安德鲁斯·史坦因]]), Walter ([[安顿·瓦尔特|安顿·瓦尔特]]), Graf ([[康拉德·葛雷夫|康拉德·葛雷夫]]), Buchholtz ([[弗雷德里克·布克霍尔茨|弗雷德里克·布克霍尔茨]]) instruments made by Paul McNulty ([[保罗·麦克诺提|保罗·麦克诺提]]). Label: Moscow Conservatory Records.
* Beethoven: Piano Sonatas - No.8, Op.13 “Pathetique”; No. 14, Op.27, No.2 “Moonlight”; No.21, Op.53 “Waldstein” in C Major; No.27. Recorded on an antique fortepiano John Broadwood & Son 1806 restored by Cristopher Clarke. Label: Erato.
* 阿列克谢·卢比莫夫、阿列克谢·祖耶夫。Claude Debussy. Preludes. Recorded on Steinway 1913 and Bechstein 1925. Label: ECM Records.
* 阿列克谢·卢比莫夫，凯勒四重奏。Lento — Alfred Schnittke, Dmitri Shostakovich. Recorded on a modern piano. Label: ECM Records.
* 丹尼斯·拉塞尔·戴维斯（指挥）、阿列克谢·卢比莫夫（钢琴）、维也纳交响乐团。Valentin Silvestrov: Metamusik/Postludum. Label: ECM Records.

